{
  "stem": "23278.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we went-- I went out with the [GERMAN], you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were playing the guitar, singing song, picnics, flowers everywhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Order.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything was clean.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The old people were very respected, not like in the-- in the sub-- in the-- you know, in the bus, on Broadway, where all the kids take the seats and the older people stand.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, kids here have absolutely no education whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, it's shameful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there, the old-- we had to give our seat to older people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "To me, it was a paradise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Germany, 1936.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course it was made for the Olympic Games with the sign of Wilkommen, Welcome, Bienvenue everywhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Flowers.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You had no idea what was cooking up there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I came back to-- to France with a fantastic impression.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know me was always kept with my school work and all that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was sport, they were singing, they were outing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And me, I came back to my French gray life, all work and no fun at all.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I remember that interlude in Germany as being something marvelous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We went to Berlin, and then I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I recounted afterwards what we did there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my father had gone to make contact with-- with Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And those Jewish family were extremely German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "For instance, because I was French and my father was French, they wanted to treat us well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were very rich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had servants.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they served us asparagus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Maybe it makes you smile, but at the time of Hitler, you just didn't grow asparagus because it was a wasteful food, a non-nourishing food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the servant brought a dish of asparagus, and the kids, I mean, they were little neighbors or friends.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
